    "body": "My parents keep making comments about how we're doing our kids a disservice by homeschooling. 'You're not qualified,' 'they need socialization,' 'they'll fall behind.' We're actually thriving but I'm so tired of defending our choice. How do you handle family that doesn't support your decision?",
